## 4. PERFORMANCE & CORE WEB VITALS

### üñºÔ∏è IMAGE OPTIMIZATION (LCP)

**MANDATORY: Use `next/image` with proper attributes:**
```tsx
import Image from 'next/image';

// ‚ùå WRONG - Regular img tag
<img src="/brain-scan.jpg" alt="MRI scan" />

// ‚úÖ CORRECT - Next.js Image with optimization
<Image
  src="/brain-scan.jpg"
  alt="Axial T2-weighted MRI showing hyperintense lesion in basal ganglia"
  width={800}
  height={600}
  priority={true}  // For above-the-fold images (LCP)
  quality={85}     // Balance quality vs. file size
  placeholder="blur" // Prevents layout shift
  blurDataURL="data:image/jpeg;base64,..." // Optional: custom blur
/>
```

**Image Attribute Rules:**
- `priority={true}` ‚Üí For hero images, article headers (first visible image)
- `priority={false}` ‚Üí For below-the-fold content
- Always include descriptive `alt` text (not just "image" or "photo")
- Use `sizes` prop for responsive images

### ‚úçÔ∏è FONT OPTIMIZATION (CLS)

**MANDATORY: Use `next/font` to prevent layout shift:**
```tsx
// app/layout.tsx

import { Inter, Space_Grotesk } from 'next/font/google';

const inter = Inter({
  subsets: ['latin'],
  variable: '--font-inter',
  display: 'swap', // Prevent FOIT (Flash of Invisible Text)
});

const spaceGrotesk = Space_Grotesk({
  subsets: ['latin'],
  variable: '--font-heading',
  display: 'swap',
  weight: ['700'],
});

export default function RootLayout({ children }) {
  return (
    <html lang="en" className={`${inter.variable} ${spaceGrotesk.variable}`}>
      <body>{children}</body>
    </html>
  );
}
```

**In CSS:**
```css
body {
  font-family: var(--font-inter), sans-serif;
}

h1, h2, h3 {
  font-family: var(--font-heading), sans-serif;
}
```

### ‚ö° LAZY LOADING

**For non-critical content:**
```tsx
import dynamic from 'next/dynamic';

// Lazy load heavy components
const InteractiveQuiz = dynamic(() => import('@/components/InteractiveQuiz'), {
  loading: () => <div>Loading quiz...</div>,
  ssr: false, // Client-side only if needed
});

// Lazy load images below the fold
<Image
  src="/diagram.png"
  alt="Neural pathway diagram"
  width={600}
  height={400}
  loading="lazy" // Defers loading until near viewport
/>
```

### üìä CORE WEB VITALS TARGETS

**Aim for these scores:**

- **LCP (Largest Contentful Paint):** < 2.5s
- **FID (First Input Delay):** < 100ms
- **CLS (Cumulative Layout Shift):** < 0.1

**Monitor with:**
```bash
npm run build
npm run start
# Open Lighthouse in Chrome DevTools
```

